name: Natural Gentle Milk Cleanser 5oz
description: A rich milky cleanser that hydrates as it gently cleanses away dirt and impurities. Removes makeup and daily residue while leaving the skin perfectly nourished. Ingredients: Aqua, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Glycerin, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) Fruit Oil, Sodium Bis-Hydroxyethylglycinate Coco-Glucosides Crosspolymer, Althaea Officinalis (Marshmallow) Root Extract, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Acrylates/C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate Crosspolymer, PEG-100 Stearate, Glyceryl Stearate, Polysorbate-20, Aminomethyl Propanediol, Xanthan Gum, Ethylhexylglycerin
